|ap_ready    | out |    1| ap_ctrl_hs |  CNN_ALU_Top | return value |
|rs1_data_V  |  in |   32|   ap_none  |  rs1_data_V  |    scalar    |
|cnn_op_V    |  in |    4|   ap_none  |   cnn_op_V   |    scalar    |
|rd_data_V   | out |   32|   ap_none  |   rd_data_V  |    pointer   |
+------------+-----+-----+------------+--------------+--------------+

